OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe new leader of Bradford City
OL,8,Fcouncil has set out his priorities
OL,9,Fincluding action on the clean air zone
OL,10,Fand an inquiry into rape gangs.
OL,12,FReform UK councillor Stephen Place was
OL,13,Felected last week, Tuesday 19 May, as
OL,14,Fthe leader of one of Yorkshire's
OL,15,Flargest councils.
OL,17,FThe former police officer told ITV
OL,18,FCalendar: "I've been asking in
OL,19,FBradford for an inquiry into rape
OL,20,Fgangs since 2014.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"It's a major issue in this city and
OL,8,FI, along with other people believe
OL,9,Fthat, if the real facts were known,
OL,10,Fthe numbers involved would dwarf
OL,11,FRochdale, Rotherham, Telford. So we
OL,12,Fhave to drill into it.
OL,14,F"The survivors of the rape gangs need
OL,15,Fto have their voices heard, and so it
OL,16,Fis imperative that we are part of that
OL,17,Fnational inquiry."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FCllr Place also spoke about the city's
OL,8,Fcontroversial clean air scheme
OL,9,Fpraising it's effectiveness but
OL,10,Fpledging to scrap charges.
OL,12,FHe said: "I think it's done its job,
OL,13,Fand it says within the business model
OL,14,Fthat once it has achieved its aims it
OL,15,Fwill stop, and I think it's achieved
OL,16,Fits aims and so we'll stop it.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"Wakefield, Calderdale, Kirklees,
OL,8,FBarnsley, they never did it - It was
OL,9,Fonly Bradford that did it and my firm
OL,10,Fbelief is that they did it because it
OL,11,Fwas a cash cow."
OL,13,FCllr Place also stressed his want for
OL,14,Fa positive outlook for Bradford
OL,15,Fadding: "We are positive about
OL,16,FBradford, we want Bradford open for
OL,17,Fbusiness, we've got a terrific
OL,18,Ffootball team, we've got a wonderful
OL,19,Fpopulation, it's a beautiful city."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FHowever, Reform UK have faced calls to
OL,8,Fsuspend Cllr Place from the party over
OL,9,Falleged racist and misogynistic social
OL,10,Fmedia posts unearthed by 'Reform Party
OL,11,FUK Exposed' on X (formerly Twitter).
OL,13,FLabour MP for Shipley Anna Dixon wrote
OL,14,Fto Reform UK leader Nigel Farage
OL,15,Fraising what she called "serious
OL,16,Fconcerns" over the appointment of Cllr
OL,17,FPlace as leader.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FIn the letter she said: "a number of
OL,8,Fposts made by Mr Place on his public
OL,9,FInstagram account (@stephenplace50)
OL,10,Fmade between November 2023 and
OL,11,FDecember 2025 have been brought to my
OL,12,Fattention."
OL,14,FWhen asked about the posts Cllr Place
OL,15,Fsaid: "This is a nonsense from 4 or 5
OL,16,Fyears ago. I had a big open Facebook
OL,17,Fpage, people put things on there, I
OL,18,Fput things on there.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"Did I police it? No, probably not,
OL,8,Fthat's the end of it as far as I'm
OL,9,Fconcerned, this is about Bradford, my
OL,10,Fvision for Bradford.
OL,12,F"Let's just move on and let's talk
OL,13,Fabout Bradford and the plan and the
OL,14,Fvision for reform."
OL,16,FIn the local elections earlier this
OL,17,Fmonth Reform won enough seats to
OL,18,Fbecome the largest party on the
OL,19,Fcouncil winning 29 seats. Far below
OL,20,Fthe 46 seats a party needs for an
OL,21,Foverall majority.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThis meant Cllr Place's path to become
OL,8,Fleader was far from straight forward.
OL,10,FWhen time came to vote for a new
OL,11,Fleader all 28 Reform members voted in
OL,12,Ffavour of Cllr Place.
OL,14,FBut there were 35 votes from other
OL,15,Fparties against his appointment
OL,16,Fmeaning Cllr Place lost the vote.
OL,18,FReform then nominated both Cllr Place
OL,19,Fand Councillor Andrew Judson (Reform,
OL,20,FKeighley West) as potential leaders.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThis time Cllr Place received 28
OL,8,Fvotes, all from his Reform colleagues,
OL,9,Fwhile Cllr Judson received none.
OL,11,FEvery other member on the 90 strong
OL,12,FCouncil abstained from voting `
OL,13,Fmeaning Cllr Place was elected leader
OL,14,Fof Bradford Council.
OL,16,FReform UK's number has fallen to 28
OL,17,Fafter the suspension of Councillor
OL,18,FDaniel Devaney (Clayton and
OL,19,FFairweather Green) over social media
OL,20,Fposts.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779970272
OL,3,CBradford Council's Leader says city
OL,4,Cmust be involved in grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FCllr Devaney has since said he
OL,8,Fregretted making the posts.
OL,10,FWhen asked about the suspension Cllr
OL,11,FPlace said: "Yeah, he's apologised for
OL,12,Fit, but he's not a Reform councillor,
OL,13,Fhe's an independent councillor.
OL,15,F"People slipped through the net, I
OL,16,Fthink about 8,500 people were vetted.
OL,18,F"The party's admitted that the vetting
OL,19,Fprocesses need to be more rigorous."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
